# SeaDrop Deployment

For official deployments see [Deployments](../README.md#deployments).

If you would like to deploy your own `SeaDrop` instance, you can do so with:

`forge create --rpc-url ${RPC_URL} src/SeaDrop.sol:SeaDrop --private-key ${PK} --etherscan-api-key ${ETHERSCAN_API_KEY} --verify`

To deploy at the cross-chain address of `0x00005EA00Ac477B1030CE78506496e8C2dE24bf5`, send:

```
cast send --rpc-url ${RPC_URL} --private-key ${PK} 0x0000000000ffe8b47b3e2130213b802212439497 
```

The SeaDrop version above is tagged on GitHub as [`seadrop-1.0`](https://github.com/ProjectOpenSea/seadrop/releases/tag/seadrop-1.0).
